venue.name: East bay Bike Path

item.description: Hello! Last meetup for this ride cancelled because of weather. This is a ride of 5 miles from Warren to Bristol each way, and if other members want to they can ride longer as this is a great place to ride,and it's so much more fun to ride with a group of awesome people, including hipsters,A-listers, bored Euro -Trash, and recent parole's from club Fed! Sounds Cool doesn't it? Hopefully weather will co-operate this time, I look forward to seeing you there!
item.name: Reschuled Meetup, East Bay Bike Path, Warren, R.I. to Bristol R.I.
